==English==
=== Verb ===
'''detrain'''

#to [[exit]] from a [[train]]; to [[disembark]]
#:''If you plan to '''detrain''' at the next stop, please begin gathering your belongings.''

# For an [[athlete]], to reduce one's [[training]], particularly during the [[offseason]], in preparation for a cycle of [[retraining]].  Note, detraining is not common in [[tae kwon do]].

